	<div class="grid_7">
		<br/><h2 id="features" class="ir"><em>Features</em></h2>
        <p>The main contributions:
        <ul>
            <li>Novel <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijch4.html">relevance feedback methods</a></li>
            <li>Extensive comparison of <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijse21.html">pseudo</a> and <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijse22.html">explicit</a> relevance feedback methods</li>
            <li><a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijch5.html">Concept-based query modeling</a></li>
            <li>Novel method for <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijch6.html">linking queries to concept languages</a></li>
            <li>Understanding of <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijse33.html">relevant features for concept identification</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijch7.html">Wikipedia-based query modeling</a></li>
            <li>State of the art retrieval effectiveness on <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/thesis-emeijse16.html">an extensive set of test collections</a></li>
            <li><em>And a <a href="http://phdthes.is/html-edition/">LOT</a> more...</em></li>
        </ul>
        </p>
